<title>BCM_GETWORDLENGTH</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>BCM_GETWORDLENGTH</strong></font></p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#E6E6E6"><pre>BCM_GETWORDLENGTH
	wParam = 0;
	lParam = 0;</pre>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>Get the size in bytes required to store the word under the caret.</p>

<ul>
    <li>Returns the size, in bytes, required to hold the word under the caret.</li>
</ul>

<dl>
	<dt><strong>Notes:</strong><dt>
	<dd>The returned size does not include a terminating 0 byte.<br>
	When the caret is not located on a word the message will
	return 0.
	</dd>
</dl>

</body>
